title: American Horror Stories (OFFICIAL AHS Spin-off)
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: I have a love hate relationship with AHS promotional videos, especially when they outright lie to me. Each fantastical tease of an idea that goes nowhere when the season actually starts, leaves me feeling like a scorned lover. 😉🖤
The music playing with this shot.....chilling!! 🖤
I have no idea what’s in store for this spin off but I’m sooooo excited
I'm so clueless and I love it, usually I can figure stuff out but I'm a blank slate right now.
